    </entry>
    <entry>
      <string>Description</string>
      <string>RAM-backed iterative 8x8 multiplier. High byte=multiplier (control), low byte=multiplicand (data). Shift-and-add into register accumulator, output through tri-state driver.</string>
    </entry>
